      • getProgress

        public String getProgress(long date,
                 long gId,
                 String token,
                 String username)
        Get progress report for specified goal
        Parameters:
        date - - progress checking date
        gId - - goal id
        username - id of a user
        token - authentication token generated while the user logs in
        Returns:
        -2 Red - means needs more than 160% rate to achieve goal from initial rate estimated
        -1 Yellow - means needs up to 160% rate to achieve a goal
        0 Green - means progress on track
        Response 204 - if goal doesn't exist
